  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Constructing InicioTab Component**\n\nI\'m making swift progress on the `InicioTab` component, `src/components/InicioTab.tsx`. Currently, I\'m focusing on the checkout state (\"Fora de jornada\"). My goal is to build the status card featuring the \"STATUS ATUAL - Voc\303\252 est\303\241 fora de jornada\" message alongside the moon icon, and a circular \"CHECK-IN\" button with a play icon.\n\n\n**Defining Check-In Functionality**\n\nI\'m now fully immersed in defining the check-in functionality. The \"CHECK-IN\" button needs a vibrant, glowing yellow aura to convey the start. The location box will feature \"Posto Graal - KM 120\" with a `MapPin` icon. The form section requires an input field for \"QUILOMETRAGEM ATUAL\" with a speed/gauge icon. A button section will present a grid of four options: CARGA, DESCARGA, DESCANSO, QUEBRA, with active selection highlighted in safety yellow. I\'m building it to be fully interactive.\n\n\n**Designing Journey UI**\n\nI\'m now designing the user interface for when the driver is \"EM JORNADA\". There\'s a status card with a yellow background, displaying \"EM JORNADA\" and \"ESTADIA ATIVA\", featuring a prominent ticking clock (or moon icon). The UI will present the location information, and a large, red \"CHECK-OUT\" button. A summary card at the bottom will display the chosen reason, odometer value, and start time. On checkout, the UI calculates and displays the total elapsed time, stops the clock, stores it to history, switches back to outside journey, and provides a success confirmation.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will design and create the `InicioTab` component (`src/components/InicioTab.tsx`). This component implements both states (Checked-Out and Checked-In). In Checked-Out mode, the driver inputs current mileage, selects a stop reason, and presses \"CHECK-IN\". In Checked-In mode, a live chronometer ticks every second, a summary card shows information, and a large red \"CHECK-OUT\" button logs out, submitting a new entry to the historical log database automatically."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 5
      nanos: 536216298
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
