    modified_response: "I will design and create the `HistoricoTab` component (`src/components/HistoricoTab.tsx`). It features dynamic filters (\"HOJE\", \"ESTA SEMANA\", \"M\303\212S\") which actively filter the driver\'s logs. The items follow a Bento-style card layout, with chromatic status stripes indicating categories (Green for Descanso/Refei\303\247\303\243o, Yellow for Carga, Orange for Descarga, Red for Quebra/Manuten\303\247\303\243o), displaying durations."
