    thinking: "**Defining Prop Requirements**\n\nI\'m currently working on incorporating the `DriverProfile` into `/src/components/HistoricoTab.tsx` as a prop within `HistoricoTabProps`. Additionally, I\'m setting up state using `useState` to manage a selected history entry, initially set to `null`. This will enable tracking of selected reports.\n\n\n**Implementing Report Selection**\n\nI\'ve implemented the `onClick` handler to set the selected report. Now, I\'m focusing on rendering a dialog/modal with detailed information once a report is selected. It will display driver details like name, CNH/CPF, vehicle information, and stay details from the `selectedReport`, while building fallbacks for initial entries. I\'ll need to figure out how to calculate stay durations.\n\n\n**Designing Report Modal**\n\nI\'ve established fallbacks to ensure compatibility and smooth rendering. Now, I\'m concentrating on the design of the modal component for reports, which will display detailed stay information. A key feature will be a copyable text button that allows the driver to easily forward a report to other stakeholders. I\'m currently drafting the plain text content of the report to be copied.\n\n\n"
