    instruction: "Atualizar a listagem de cart\303\265es de hist\303\263rico com indica\303\247\303\243o visual de f\303\263rmula e reformular o Modal de Cobran\303\247a com as tabelas da ANTT e regras de exclus\303\243o das 5 primeiras horas no HistoricoTab.tsx"
    replacement_infos {
      original_chunk {
        target_content: "      {/* 3. REPORT EXCEL/PDF BILLING DRAWER OVERLAY (MODAL) */}\n      {selectedReport && (() => {\n        const rate = selectedReport.hourlyRate || 50.00;\n        const durHours = selectedReport.durationHoursNum || (selectedReport.id === \'h2\' ? 4.33 : (selectedReport.id === \'h3\' ? 2.75 : 1.08));\n        const finalAmt = selectedReport.totalAmount || (durHours * rate);\n        const reportTitle = `RELAT\303\223RIO DE COBRAN\303\207A - ESTADIA ${selectedReport.type}`;\n\n        const textToCopy = `--- RELAT\303\223RIO PARA ENVIO DE COBRAN\303\207A (ESTADIA/DEMURRAGE) ---\nID DO REGISTRO: ${selectedReport.id}\nEMISS\303\203O: ${new Date().toLocaleDateString(\'pt-BR\')}\n\nDADOS DO MOTORISTA:\n\342\200\242 Nome Completo: ${profile.fullName}\n\342\200\242 CPF: ${profile.cpf}\n\342\200\242 CNH: ${profile.cnh}\n\nDADOS DO VE\303\215CULO:\n\342\200\242 Modelo do Cavalo: ${profile.truckModel}\n\342\200\242 Placa Cavalo: ${profile.plateCavalo}\n\342\200\242 Placa Carreta: ${profile.plateCarreta}\n\nDETALHES DA ESTADIA:\n\342\200\242 Local do Estabelecimento: ${selectedReport.location}\n\342\200\242 Data do Registro: ${selectedReport.date}\n\342\200\242 Atividade Realizada: ${selectedReport.type}\n\342\200\242 Hor\303\241rio de Entrada: ${selectedReport.startTime}\n\342\200\242 Hor\303\241rio de Sa\303\255da: ${selectedReport.endTime || \'N\303\243o registrado\'}\n\nDEMONSTRATIVO DE VALORES:\n\342\200\242 Tempo Total: ${selectedReport.duration} (${durHours.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\')} horas decimais)\n\342\200\242 Valor Combinado por Hora: R$ ${rate.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })}\n\342\200\242 VALOR TOTAL DA COBRAN\303\207A: R$ ${finalAmt.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })}\n\n---------------------------------------------------\nGerado eletronicamente via Painel de Controle Log\303\255stica PRO.`;\n\n        const handleCopy = () => {\n          navigator.clipboard.writeText(textToCopy);\n          setCopied(true);\n          setTimeout(() => setCopied(false), 2000);\n        };\n\n        return (\n          <div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-background/80 backdrop-blur-md animate-fade-in\">\n            <div className=\"bg-surface-elevated border border-outline-variant/50 w-full max-w-lg rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl flex flex-col max-h-[90vh]\">\n              \n              {/* Header */}\n              <div className=\"bg-surface-card border-b border-outline-variant/30 px-6 py-4.5 flex justify-between items-center shrink-0\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                  <div className=\"w-10 h-10 bg-safety-yellow/10 text-safety-yellow rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\">\n                    <FileText className=\"w-5.5 h-5.5\" />\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h4 className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-base text-on-surface leading-tight uppercase\">\n                      Faturamento de Estadia\n                    </h4>\n                    <p className=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant tracking-wider uppercase mt-0.5\">\n                      Ficha de Cobran\303\247a de Demurrage\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <button \n                  onClick={() => setSelectedReport(null)}\n                  className=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full hover:bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer transition-colors\"\n                >\n                  <X className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Scrollable Receipt Body */}\n              <div className=\"p-6 overflow-y-auto space-y-6 text-sm\">\n                \n                {/* Print Banner */}\n                <div className=\"bg-background-highest/30 p-4 rounded-2xl border-2 border-dashed border-outline-variant/50 text-center flex flex-col items-center\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] bg-safety-yellow text-primary-container font-mono font-extrabold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest mb-1.5 leading-none\">\n                    LEI DO MOTORISTA / EXCESSO\n                  </span>\n                  <p className=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase text-on-surface-variant tracking-wider\">\n                    VALOR DE RECLAMA\303\207\303\203O DE PERMAN\303\212NCIA\n                  </p>\n                  <p className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-2xl text-safety-yellow mt-1\">\n                    R$ {finalAmt.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })}\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Driver Context Info block */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-1\">\n                    <User className=\"w-4 h-4 text-primary-container shrink-0\" />\n                    <span className=\"font-mono text-[11px] text-primary-container font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">QUALIFICA\303\207\303\203O DO MOTORISTA</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-xs\">\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Nome do Motorista</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-on-surface uppercase mt-0.5\">{profile.fullName}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">CPF / CPF de Cadastro</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-mono font-semibold text-on-surface mt-0.5\">{profile.cpf}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Registro CNH</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-mono font-semibold text-on-surface mt-0.5\">{profile.cnh}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Gera\303\247\303\243o do Relat\303\263rio</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-medium text-on-surface mt-0.5\">{new Date().toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\')}</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Truck context detail block */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-1\">\n                    <TruckIcon className=\"w-4 h-4 text-primary-container shrink-0\" />\n                    <span className=\"font-mono text-[11px] text-primary-container font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">RELA\303\207\303\203O VEICULAR</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-xs\">\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Cavalo Trator</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-on-surface uppercase mt-0.5\">{profile.truckModel}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Placa Cavalo</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-mono font-bold text-safety-yellow mt-0.5 uppercase bg-surface-container/60 text-center py-0.5 rounded\">\n                        {profile.plateCavalo}\n                      </p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Placa Carreta</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-mono font-bold text-safety-yellow mt-0.5 uppercase bg-surface-container/60 text-center py-0.5 rounded\">\n                        {profile.plateCarreta}\n                      </p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Stay log detail list */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-1\">\n                    <Calendar className=\"w-4 h-4 text-primary-container shrink-0\" />\n                    <span className=\"font-mono text-[11px] text-primary-container font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">APURA\303\207\303\203O DA ESTADIA</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-3 text-xs\">\n                    <div className=\"col-span-2\">\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Estabelecimento / Local de Repouso/Espera</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-on-surface text-sm mt-0.5\">{selectedReport.location}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Entrada Registrada</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-bold text-on-surface mt-0.5 uppercase\">{selectedReport.startTime}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Sa\303\255da Conclu\303\255da</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-bold text-on-surface mt-0.5 uppercase\">{selectedReport.endTime || \'Fim de Jornada\'}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Atividade / Finalidade</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-mono font-bold text-primary-container uppercase mt-0.5\">{selectedReport.type}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Data Declarada</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-medium text-on-surface mt-0.5\">{selectedReport.date}</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Calculation demonstrative block */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-2 bg-surface-container rounded-2xl p-4 border border-outline-variant/30\">\n                  <p className=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant uppercase font-bold tracking-widest text-center border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-1.5 mb-2\">\n                    DEMONSTRATIVO DE C\303\201LCULO DE VALOR\n                  </p>\n                  \n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-sans\">\n                    <span className=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Quantidade Horas Totais (Decimal)</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-on-surface\">{durHours.toFixed(2)}h (${selectedReport.duration})</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-sans\">\n                    <span className=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Valor da Hora Ajustado</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-on-surface\">R$ {rate.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"h-px bg-outline-variant/30 my-2\"></div>\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                    <span className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-on-surface text-sm\">TOTAL A SER FATURADO</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-mono font-extrabold text-base text-safety-yellow\">\n                      R$ {finalAmt.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Copy / billing button interaction footer */}\n              <div className=\"bg-surface-card border-t border-outline-variant/30 p-4 flex gap-3 shrink-0\">\n                <button\n                  onClick={handleCopy}\n                  className={`flex-1 h-12 rounded-xl font-mono text-xs uppercase font-extrabold tracking-wider transition-all duration-200 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 cursor-pointer shadow-md ${\n                    copied \n                      ? \'bg-status-success text-on-surface\' \n                      : \'bg-primary-container hover:bg-safety-yellow text-on-primary hover:text-primary-container\'\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  {copied ? (\n                    <>\n                      <Check className=\"w-4.5 h-4.5\" /> RELAT\303\223RIO COPIADO!\n                    </>\n                  ) : (\n                    <>\n                      <Copy className=\"w-4.5 h-4.5\" /> COPIAR RELAT\303\223RIO\n                    </>\n                  )}\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => setSelectedReport(null)}\n                  className=\"h-12 px-5 bg-surface-container-high hover:bg-surface-container-highest text-on-surface font-sans text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-wider rounded-xl transition-all duration-150 cursor-pointer\"\n                >\n                  Fechar\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        );\n      })()}"
        replacement_content: "      {/* 3. REPORT EXCEL/PDF BILLING DRAWER OVERLAY (MODAL) */}\n      {selectedReport && (() => {\n        const rate = selectedReport.hourlyRate || 50.00;\n        const durHours = selectedReport.durationHoursNum || (selectedReport.id === \'h2\' ? 4.33 : (selectedReport.id === \'h3\' ? 2.75 : 1.08));\n        const finalAmt = selectedReport.totalAmount || (durHours * rate);\n        \n        const isAntt = selectedReport.billingType === \'ANTT\';\n        // Old preloaded history items didn\'t have excludeFirst5Hours saved, default them to false so math is consistent!\n        const isExcluding = selectedReport.excludeFirst5Hours ?? false;\n        const capacityTons = selectedReport.truckCapacityTons ?? 12;\n        const billedHours = isExcluding ? Math.max(0, durHours - 5) : durHours;\n\n        const reportTitle = isAntt ? \'DETALHE DA RECLAMA\303\207\303\203O - LEI DA ESTADIA ANTT\' : \'DETALHE DA RECLAMA\303\207\303\203O - ACORDO PRIVADO\';\n\n        const textToCopy = `--- RELAT\303\223RIO PARA ENVIO DE COBRAN\303\207A (ESTADIA/DEMURRAGE) ---\nID DO REGISTRO: ${selectedReport.id}\nEMISS\303\203O: ${new Date().toLocaleDateString(\'pt-BR\')}\n\nREGRA APLICADA: ${isAntt ? \'LEI FEDERAL ANTT (R$ 2,50/ton\342\200\242h)\' : \'VALOR COMBINADO POR HORA\'}\nTOLER\303\202NCIA DE 5 HORAS: ${isExcluding ? \'APLICADA (As primeiras 5 horas de estadia foram descontadas)\' : \'N\303\203O APLICADA (Faturamento integral)\'}\n\nDADOS DO MOTORISTA:\n\342\200\242 Nome Completo: ${profile.fullName}\n\342\200\242 CPF: ${profile.cpf}\n\342\200\242 CNH: ${profile.cnh}\n\nDADOS DO VE\303\215CULO:\n\342\200\242 Modelo do Cavalo: ${profile.truckModel}\n\342\200\242 Placa Cavalo: ${profile.plateCavalo}\n\342\200\242 Placa Carreta: ${profile.plateCarreta}\n\nDETALHES DA ESTADIA:\n\342\200\242 Local do Estabelecimento: ${selectedReport.location}\n\342\200\242 Data do Registro: ${selectedReport.date}\n\342\200\242 Atividade Realizada: ${selectedReport.type}\n\342\200\242 Hor\303\241rio de Entrada: ${selectedReport.startTime}\n\342\200\242 Hor\303\241rio de Sa\303\255da: ${selectedReport.endTime || \'N\303\243o registrado\'}\n\nDEMONSTRATIVO DE VALORES:\n\342\200\242 Tempo Total Confeccionado: ${selectedReport.duration} (${durHours.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\')} horas decimais)\n\342\200\242 Horas de Isen\303\247\303\243o (Toler\303\242ncia): ${isExcluding ? \'5,00 horas\' : \'0,00 horas\'}\n\342\200\242 Tempo Efetivo de Cobran\303\247a: ${billedHours.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\')} horas\n${isAntt ? `\342\200\242 Capacidade de Carga Homologada: ${capacityTons} toneladas\\n\342\200\242 Taxa da ANTT: R$ 2,50 por tonelada/hora` : `\342\200\242 Valor Combinado Contratado: R$ ${rate.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })} por hora`}\n\342\200\242 VALOR TOTAL DA COBRAN\303\207A: R$ ${finalAmt.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })}\n\n---------------------------------------------------\nGerado eletronicamente conforme Lei n\302\272 11.442/2007 via Painel de Controle Log\303\255stica PRO.`;\n\n        const handleCopy = () => {\n          navigator.clipboard.writeText(textToCopy);\n          setCopied(true);\n          setTimeout(() => setCopied(false), 2000);\n        };\n\n        return (\n          <div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-background/80 backdrop-blur-md animate-fade-in\">\n            <div className=\"bg-surface-elevated border border-outline-variant/50 w-full max-w-lg rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl flex flex-col max-h-[90vh]\">\n              \n              {/* Header */}\n              <div className=\"bg-surface-card border-b border-outline-variant/30 px-6 py-4.5 flex justify-between items-center shrink-0\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                  <div className=\"w-10 h-10 bg-safety-yellow/10 text-safety-yellow rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\">\n                    <FileText className=\"w-5.5 h-5.5\" />\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h4 className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-base text-on-surface leading-tight uppercase\">\n                      {isAntt ? \'Faturamento Lei ANTT/11.442\' : \'Faturamento de Estadia\'}\n                    </h4>\n                    <p className=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant tracking-wider uppercase mt-0.5\">\n                      {isAntt ? \'Demonstrativo de Demurrage Federal\' : \'Ficha de Cobran\303\247a Combinada\'}\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <button \n                  onClick={() => setSelectedReport(null)}\n                  className=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full hover:bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer transition-colors\"\n                >\n                  <X className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Scrollable Receipt Body */}\n              <div className=\"p-6 overflow-y-auto space-y-6 text-sm\">\n                \n                {/* Print Banner */}\n                <div className=\"bg-background-highest/30 p-4 rounded-2xl border-2 border-dashed border-outline-variant/50 text-center flex flex-col items-center\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] bg-safety-yellow text-primary-container font-mono font-extrabold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest mb-1.5 leading-none\">\n                    {isAntt ? \'LEI 11.442/2007 GARANTIDA\' : \'VALOR COMBINADO\'}\n                  </span>\n                  <p className=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase text-on-surface-variant tracking-wider\">\n                    VALOR DE RECLAMA\303\207\303\203O DE PERMAN\303\212NCIA\n                  </p>\n                  <p className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-2xl text-safety-yellow mt-1\">\n                    R$ {finalAmt.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })}\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Driver Context Info block */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-1\">\n                    <User className=\"w-4 h-4 text-primary-container shrink-0\" />\n                    <span className=\"font-mono text-[11px] text-primary-container font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">QUALIFICA\303\207\303\203O DO MOTORISTA</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-xs\">\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Nome do Motorista</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-on-surface uppercase mt-0.5\">{profile.fullName}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">CPF de Cadastro</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-mono font-semibold text-on-surface mt-0.5\">{profile.cpf}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Registro CNH</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-mono font-semibold text-on-surface mt-0.5\">{profile.cnh}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Gera\303\247\303\243o do Relat\303\263rio</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-medium text-on-surface mt-0.5\">{new Date().toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\')}</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Truck context detail block */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-1\">\n                    <TruckIcon className=\"w-4 h-4 text-primary-container shrink-0\" />\n                    <span className=\"font-mono text-[11px] text-primary-container font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">RELA\303\207\303\203O VEICULAR</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-xs\">\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Cavalo Trator</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-on-surface uppercase mt-0.5\">{profile.truckModel}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Placa Cavalo</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-mono font-bold text-safety-yellow mt-0.5 uppercase bg-surface-container/60 text-center py-0.5 rounded\">\n                        {profile.plateCavalo}\n                      </p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Placa Carreta</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-mono font-bold text-safety-yellow mt-0.5 uppercase bg-surface-container/60 text-center py-0.5 rounded\">\n                        {profile.plateCarreta}\n                      </p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Stay log detail list */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-1\">\n                    <Calendar className=\"w-4 h-4 text-primary-container shrink-0\" />\n                    <span className=\"font-mono text-[11px] text-primary-container font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">APURA\303\207\303\203O DA ESTADIA</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-3 text-xs\">\n                    <div className=\"col-span-2\">\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Estabelecimento / Local de Repouso/Espera</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-on-surface text-sm mt-0.5\">{selectedReport.location}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Entrada Registrada</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-bold text-on-surface mt-0.5 uppercase\">{selectedReport.startTime}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Sa\303\255da Conclu\303\255da</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-bold text-on-surface mt-0.5 uppercase\">{selectedReport.endTime || \'Fim de Jornada\'}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Atividade / Finalidade</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-mono font-bold text-primary-container uppercase mt-0.5\">{selectedReport.type}</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <p className=\"text-on-surface-variant font-sans\">Data Declarada</p>\n                      <p className=\"font-sans font-medium text-on-surface mt-0.5\">{selectedReport.date}</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Calculation demonstrative block */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-2 bg-surface-container rounded-2xl p-4 border border-outline-variant/30\">\n                  <p className=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant uppercase font-bold tracking-widest text-center border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-1.5 mb-2\">\n                    DEMONSTRATIVO DE C\303\201LCULO DE VALOR\n                  </p>\n                  \n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-sans\">\n                    <span className=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Tempo Decorrido Total</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-on-surface\">{selectedReport.duration} ({durHours.toFixed(2)}h decimais)</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-sans\">\n                    <span className=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Car\303\252ncia/Toler\303\242ncia Descontada</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-on-surface\">{isExcluding ? \'-5,00 horas\' : \'0,00 horas\'}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-sans\">\n                    <span className=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Tempo Cobr\303\241vel Excedente</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-safety-yellow\">{billedHours.toFixed(2)}h</span>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {isAntt ? (\n                    <>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-sans\">\n                        <span className=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Capacidade de Carga do Ve\303\255culo</span>\n                        <span className=\"font-bold text-on-surface\">{capacityTons} Toneladas</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-sans\">\n                        <span className=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Taxa Oficial ANTT (Lei 11.442)</span>\n                        <span className=\"font-bold text-on-surface\">R$ 2,50 / Tonelada \342\200\242 hora</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </>\n                  ) : (\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-sans\">\n                      <span className=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Valor Combinado Ajustado</span>\n                      <span className=\"font-bold text-on-surface\">R$ {rate.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })}/hora</span>\n                    </div>\n                  )}\n\n                  <div className=\"h-px bg-outline-variant/30 my-2\"></div>\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                    <div className=\"flex flex-col\">\n                      <span className=\"font-sans font-extrabold text-on-surface text-sm\">TOTAL A SER COBRADO</span>\n                      {isAntt && (\n                        <span className=\"text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant font-mono mt-0.5\">F\303\263rmula: {billedHours.toFixed(2)}h x {capacityTons}t x R$ 2,50</span>\n                      )}\n                    </div>\n                    <span className=\"font-mono font-extrabold text-base text-safety-yellow\">\n                      R$ {finalAmt.toLocaleString(\'pt-BR\', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Important Law Rules Notice Card */}\n                {isAntt && (\n                  <div className=\"bg-safety-yellow/5 border border-safety-yellow/20 p-4 rounded-xl text-xs space-y-1.5 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">\n                    <p className=\"font-semibold text-safety-yellow uppercase text-[10px] tracking-wider mb-1\">\360\237\224\227 Regras Legais Importantes</p>\n                    <p>\342\200\242 <b>Comprovante de Chegada:</b> O embarcador e destinat\303\241rio s\303\243o obrigados a fornecer documento atestando hor\303\241rio exato de chegada. A falta pode gerar multa de at\303\251 <span className=\"text-safety-yellow/90 font-bold\">5% do valor da carga</span>.</p>\n                    <p>\342\200\242 <b>Direito Legal:</b> O pagamento da estadia adicional \303\251 um direito garantido pela Lei n\302\272 11.442/2007 (tanto para TAC aut\303\264nomo quanto ETC empresa de transporte).</p>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Copy / billing button interaction footer */}\n              <div className=\"bg-surface-card border-t border-outline-variant/30 p-4 flex gap-3 shrink-0\">\n                <button\n                  onClick={handleCopy}\n                  className={`flex-1 h-12 rounded-xl font-mono text-xs uppercase font-extrabold tracking-wider transition-all duration-200 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 cursor-pointer shadow-md ${\n                    copied \n                      ? \'bg-status-success text-on-surface\' \n                      : \'bg-primary-container hover:bg-safety-yellow text-on-primary hover:text-primary-container\'\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  {copied ? (\n                    <>\n                      <Check className=\"w-4.5 h-4.5\" /> RELAT\303\223RIO COPIADO!\n                    </>\n                  ) : (\n                    <>\n                      <Copy className=\"w-4.5 h-4.5\" /> COPIAR RELAT\303\223RIO\n                    </>\n                  )}\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => setSelectedReport(null)}\n                  className=\"h-12 px-5 bg-surface-container-high hover:bg-surface-container-highest text-on-surface font-sans text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-wider rounded-xl transition-all duration-150 cursor-pointer\"\n                >\n                  Fechar\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        );\n      })()}"
      }
      num_matches: 1
